description:
Botanica by Air Wick’s Liquid Electric Diffusers use fragrances infused with natural ingredients carefully sourced in a way that respects our planet. Nature inspired. Planet conscious. Long lasting fragrance for up to 80 days (*Based on 12 hours daily usage on minimum setting).

Indulge your senses with warm & creamy coconut, patchouli, and a touch of sweet florals.

The patchouli oil in this fragrance is responsibly sources from the Indonesian exotic island of Sulawesi, carefully harvested to protect the rich mystical scent.

 

All our Botanica fragrances are infused with exotic natural ingredients, carefully sourced in a way that respects our planet.

 

As our flora is important to nurture, Botanica by Air Wick also works together with WWF to help save threatened native wildflower species from extinction.

 

Great fragrance: 100% Fragrance, infused with natural essential oils

Long lasting fragrance for up to 80 days*

Free from: Intentionally added acetone, dyes

Responsibly sourced natural ingredients.

We’ve partnered with WWF so we can help protect and restore native wildflowers.
name: Air Wick Botanica Plug Diffuser Coconut & Indonesian Patchouli Each
